WEBVTT

00:10.010 --> 00:12.012
Song Hui-na's contract ends
in three months.

00:12.095 --> 00:14.347
Team 1, get in touch and check with her.

00:14.848 --> 00:17.058
Any ideas for the empty Tuesday slot?

00:17.142 --> 00:20.895
We're targeting a genre that clearly
differentiates us from our competitors.

00:20.979 --> 00:24.357
For now, the most likely candidates
are Hwany and Jingom.

00:24.441 --> 00:26.693
Oh, and how's Friday coming along?

00:26.776 --> 00:30.113
Another company ran a promotion last week.
It didn't hurt us, did it?

00:30.196 --> 00:31.865
What is she up to?

00:31.948 --> 00:34.492
Yun Song suddenly went on hiatus, so…

00:34.576 --> 00:38.496
If you can't control your authors,
you should have a contingency plan!

00:38.580 --> 00:40.582
Stay sharp, or we could fall behind fast!

00:40.665 --> 00:44.085
This goes for all of you, okay?
Keep that in mind.

00:51.843 --> 00:53.928
-Thank you.
-Sure.

01:05.065 --> 01:07.067
It's finally here.

01:09.736 --> 01:11.321
-You have to go with me.
-Okay.

01:11.404 --> 01:12.655
Look, isn't it pretty?

01:13.156 --> 01:15.408
I can't wait to see it!

01:19.996 --> 01:21.331
At first, it was just

01:23.249 --> 01:24.918
a string of coincidences.

01:28.505 --> 01:31.216
I ran into her when I least expected it.

01:33.593 --> 01:34.594
Mere coincidence.

01:44.395 --> 01:46.731
Next up, Seo Mi-rae. Pick your gift.

01:47.232 --> 01:49.109
Pick a cute one!

01:49.192 --> 01:50.026
What is it?

01:52.278 --> 01:53.113
No way!

01:56.157 --> 01:58.159
-Thank you.
-It looks like you!

01:58.243 --> 02:00.411
So adorable. It looks just like you!

02:01.162 --> 02:03.540
Of all the gifts there, you picked mine.

02:05.125 --> 02:05.959
A coincidence.

02:14.092 --> 02:16.052
Every day, we got on the same elevator.

02:18.763 --> 02:19.597
A coincidence.

02:45.999 --> 02:46.833
I realized then…

02:49.294 --> 02:51.963
that I was waiting
for another coincidence.

02:55.633 --> 02:56.634
That won't work.

02:59.304 --> 03:00.138
Okay.

03:03.433 --> 03:07.020
Some days, I got a little greedy.

03:09.355 --> 03:10.732
Cliché.

03:12.108 --> 03:14.360
Not a cliché, but a classic.

03:23.077 --> 03:24.370
One iced Americano, please.

03:24.454 --> 03:26.164
And an iced latte with that.

03:32.212 --> 03:33.796
-Here to buy coffee?
-Yes.

03:33.880 --> 03:35.506
Iced latte, please.

03:35.590 --> 03:37.133
That will be 4,500 won.

03:39.928 --> 03:41.346
Thank you.

03:44.265 --> 03:47.977
Some days, I tried to act
like I didn't care and give up.

03:48.061 --> 03:50.021
Ta-da! It's this, right?

04:00.073 --> 04:00.907
There we go.

04:04.077 --> 04:06.371
But whenever I did, you would…

04:21.177 --> 04:22.595
You actually made it?

04:26.683 --> 04:28.434
…keep stepping into my side.

04:53.418 --> 04:57.922
EPISODE 7
THE ALGORITHM OF FEELINGS

05:01.050 --> 05:02.302
So warm.

05:19.360 --> 05:20.570
What are you doing here?

05:25.742 --> 05:26.617
Hello?

05:27.744 --> 05:28.619
Hello?

05:41.132 --> 05:42.133
Mr. Park…

05:46.637 --> 05:47.513
Why are you here?

05:48.097 --> 05:48.931
Oh, I…

05:49.724 --> 05:50.558
I just…

05:54.604 --> 05:58.274
I was just getting some fresh air.
I was just about to head inside.

06:00.360 --> 06:01.194
Then let's go.

06:01.277 --> 06:04.030
No, I'm good. I can go by myself.

06:04.697 --> 06:05.615
You're tipsy.

06:06.449 --> 06:08.701
I'm really fine though…

06:29.722 --> 06:31.099
Back there,

06:31.599 --> 06:34.435
you said, "You actually made it."

06:36.938 --> 06:38.189
What did you mean by that?

06:39.440 --> 06:42.026
It was probably the alcohol. I'm sorry.

06:42.110 --> 06:43.903
Did you mistake me for someone else?

06:43.986 --> 06:47.073
No. It's not like that.

06:48.574 --> 06:52.995
But weren't you drinking with the others?

06:53.496 --> 06:54.747
Why did you come out here?

06:54.831 --> 06:55.748
I just thought

06:57.041 --> 06:58.668
I might get some fresh air too.

07:05.133 --> 07:06.884
Is your relationship going well?

07:12.515 --> 07:13.349
Yes.

07:16.394 --> 07:17.562
Glad to hear it.

07:37.707 --> 07:39.208
This is my room.

07:39.792 --> 07:40.626
Okay.

07:42.211 --> 07:43.171
Good night.

07:44.422 --> 07:45.339
Good night.

08:16.621 --> 08:19.165
Kyeong-nam, where are you?
Why aren't you coming back?

08:19.248 --> 08:21.918
Dong-min's totally hammered right now.

08:22.001 --> 08:23.586
It's hilarious!

08:23.669 --> 08:25.421
Hye-bin's more drunk than I am.

08:25.505 --> 08:28.758
Did you go back to your room?
You're coming back, right?

08:33.888 --> 08:37.850
I'm tired, so I'm going to sleep now.
Have fun, everyone.

09:04.252 --> 09:07.046
Did Mi-rae pass out with Yun Song
after taking her back?

09:10.216 --> 09:12.927
Yeah. I guess I was really tired.

09:13.010 --> 09:14.220
Have fun, guys.

09:17.014 --> 09:18.558
She's always lying.

09:19.517 --> 09:21.644
Ms. Yun, I just got us a taxi.

09:21.727 --> 09:24.313
Time for you to go to your room
and go to bed. Okay?

09:24.397 --> 09:26.524
-Give me your arm.
-Let me go!

09:27.441 --> 09:31.779
Hey, why won't you ever date anyone?

09:31.862 --> 09:35.700
You had a boyfriend
back when you used to work with me.

09:35.783 --> 09:38.369
You haven't met anyone
since you broke up with him, huh?

09:40.288 --> 09:42.623
Why are you bringing that up now?

09:42.707 --> 09:46.627
Besides, how am I supposed to date anyone
when you're always giving me a hard time?

09:46.711 --> 09:52.258
If no one likes you, you should at least
have a crush on someone.

09:52.341 --> 09:55.553
I'll handle that myself, okay?
The taxi's here. Let's go.

09:55.636 --> 09:57.888
I'm going!

09:57.972 --> 10:00.641
I have two cats at home.
They're super adorable.

10:00.725 --> 10:03.352
I think I'll step outside for a bit.

10:03.436 --> 10:04.270
Huh?

10:05.605 --> 10:06.731
Don't take too long.

10:15.406 --> 10:19.160
The person you are calling
is not available. Please leave a message…

10:50.983 --> 10:52.610
CHOI DONG-MIN

10:57.782 --> 10:58.616
Hello?

10:58.699 --> 11:02.286
Kyeong-nam. Where are you, man?
Hwany is looking for you.

11:03.621 --> 11:04.747
I stepped outside and…

11:04.830 --> 11:05.831
Come back already.

11:05.915 --> 11:07.917
Come on, man. Where are you?

11:08.000 --> 11:09.418
Hey, where's Mi-rae?

11:09.502 --> 11:10.336
Huh?

11:11.253 --> 11:13.589
Mi-rae, where are you?

11:13.673 --> 11:15.675
Ms. Seo's not with you?

11:15.758 --> 11:19.929
She told Hye-bin that she left the hotel,
but she didn't come here.

11:20.012 --> 11:21.681
Where's she gone this time?

11:22.640 --> 11:23.808
Hurry back!

11:54.714 --> 11:56.757
Why do I keep getting my hopes up?

12:06.559 --> 12:09.478
I shouldn't be happy
that she doesn't have a boyfriend.

12:10.604 --> 12:12.189
Is your relationship going well?

12:15.943 --> 12:16.777
Yes.

12:17.903 --> 12:20.239
She's lying to me
about having a boyfriend.

12:21.866 --> 12:22.992
Glad to hear it.

12:24.243 --> 12:25.911
Think about what that means.

12:39.258 --> 12:41.093
It's about time I accepted it.

12:54.440 --> 12:55.775
Be right there.

12:59.236 --> 13:00.070
Ms. Yun.

13:01.113 --> 13:02.031
Let's go.

13:03.282 --> 13:04.116
What?

13:04.200 --> 13:05.201
Ms. Yun!

13:05.284 --> 13:08.329
We didn't even have breakfast.
Why are you in such a hurry?

13:08.412 --> 13:10.790
Breakfast? Who needs breakfast?

13:13.626 --> 13:15.544
You did drink too much last night--

13:15.628 --> 13:17.254
Stop talking about last night!

13:19.423 --> 13:22.009
What? Did something happen last night?

13:23.886 --> 13:25.971
I knew it. It was just a dream, wasn't it?

13:27.264 --> 13:31.018
You received an award yesterday,
and then we went for a drink…

13:31.894 --> 13:34.230
Oh, then you told Hwany--

13:34.313 --> 13:35.147
Stop!

13:37.316 --> 13:39.527
What am I going to do now? Keep up.

13:41.153 --> 13:42.363
Oh, right.

13:42.446 --> 13:45.199
Did you remember
to call your boyfriend back?

13:45.282 --> 13:46.492
What?

13:46.575 --> 13:50.204
I didn't believe you at first,
but he was gentle, with a great voice.

13:51.497 --> 13:52.623
How did you know about…

13:53.207 --> 13:56.961
While you were passed out last night,
I answered a call from your boyfriend.

13:57.044 --> 13:58.045
Hey!

13:58.712 --> 14:01.048
-Why the hell would you do that?
-What?

14:02.132 --> 14:05.261
The phone kept ringing, so I figured
someone must be very worried--

14:05.344 --> 14:07.680
You're really annoying!

14:08.973 --> 14:10.266
Ms. Yun!

14:11.517 --> 14:13.185
What's her problem?

14:24.154 --> 14:25.197
Kyeong-nam!

14:26.115 --> 14:29.326
Man, I'm dying here.
Let's go and get some gukbap.

14:29.827 --> 14:31.328
-And the others?
-Getting coffee.

14:32.997 --> 14:34.248
Here. Coffee!

14:35.541 --> 14:36.667
Mr. Park, your coffee.

14:36.750 --> 14:37.877
Thank you.

14:37.960 --> 14:39.169
Hot coffee for me.

14:40.796 --> 14:41.797
Where's Mi-rae?

14:43.799 --> 14:45.551
She and Ms. Yun left early.

14:57.688 --> 14:58.814
Hangover cure, everyone?

14:58.898 --> 15:00.149
-Sounds good.
-Let's go.

15:00.232 --> 15:01.066
Yeah.

15:01.150 --> 15:04.904
Hey, why did you leave me so early
last night?

15:04.987 --> 15:06.405
God, you reek of alcohol.

15:06.906 --> 15:08.240
Don't be like that, partner.

15:08.324 --> 15:09.742
Get away from me.

15:09.825 --> 15:11.660
Kyeong-nam, why didn't you come back?

15:11.744 --> 15:13.078
Don't be such a stranger!

15:23.339 --> 15:26.508
Sure enough, there's no place like home.

15:39.271 --> 15:40.314
DONG-MIN SENT 10 PHOTOS

15:45.361 --> 15:47.696
Looks like they had fun.

16:07.591 --> 16:09.760
-Hello?
-Did you get home safely yesterday?

16:12.262 --> 16:13.097
I did.

16:13.973 --> 16:16.392
I felt bad about
not being able to go yesterday.

16:18.018 --> 16:19.269
It's okay.

16:19.353 --> 16:22.231
I was surprised to get a call from you.

16:22.314 --> 16:24.942
I thought if I saw your face,
it'd be hard for me to leave.

16:25.025 --> 16:26.735
But I guess you weren't that sad.

16:27.695 --> 16:30.114
What do you mean? Are you going somewhere?

16:30.197 --> 16:31.448
Let's talk in person.

16:32.324 --> 16:33.242
Right now?

16:35.244 --> 16:36.328
I'll be waiting.

16:55.347 --> 16:57.391
What was that? What's going on?

16:57.474 --> 16:58.726
You're here early.

16:59.309 --> 17:00.519
Would you like a drink?

17:02.062 --> 17:02.896
No.

17:02.980 --> 17:04.314
Okay, then.

17:09.820 --> 17:11.363
So where are you going?

17:12.781 --> 17:14.658
I've been here way too long.

17:14.742 --> 17:18.370
That wasn't the plan,
but then I met a certain someone here.

17:19.621 --> 17:21.373
It's time for me to move on.

17:23.792 --> 17:25.210
Where will you be going?

17:25.294 --> 17:28.922
Nothing's decided yet.
I'll see where the road takes me.

17:30.966 --> 17:33.218
Then will you be going by yourself?

17:37.973 --> 17:39.308
Will you go with me?

17:41.977 --> 17:45.647
We can travel together,
go sightseeing, and try delicious food.

17:47.649 --> 17:50.027
I suppose you could chalk it up
to my profession,

17:50.652 --> 17:53.655
but the moment I heard those words,
I realized.

17:54.698 --> 17:55.991
I want to go with you.

17:59.119 --> 18:01.330
My journey with Gu Yeong-il

18:03.165 --> 18:06.001
was only just beginning.

18:28.816 --> 18:30.442
It'll be ready in a bit.

18:30.526 --> 18:31.902
-It looks good.
-Let's eat.

18:32.903 --> 18:34.488
Like this. Hang on.

18:37.699 --> 18:38.534
How is it?

18:47.251 --> 18:48.335
Nice and cool, huh?

19:45.225 --> 19:47.394
Come with me.

19:51.607 --> 19:52.733
What are you doing here?

20:03.076 --> 20:04.119
Why are you here?

20:05.537 --> 20:07.456
Why does that keep happening?

20:09.958 --> 20:10.792
Seo Mi-rae.

20:11.752 --> 20:12.753
Ms. Seo.

20:14.338 --> 20:15.756
Right now…

20:16.340 --> 20:17.174
What is it?

20:17.257 --> 20:18.550
Why do you do that?

20:19.259 --> 20:20.719
…who am I with?

20:35.108 --> 20:35.943
What was that?

20:36.443 --> 20:38.528
Why can't I separate the two?

20:39.571 --> 20:41.156
This isn't how it's supposed to be.

20:46.411 --> 20:49.915
I just got home. See you all tomorrow.

21:16.608 --> 21:17.442
Hello.

21:17.526 --> 21:18.360
Hi.

21:25.659 --> 21:29.746
Our company really made waves this time.
Am I right?

21:30.747 --> 21:34.668
But compared to the major platforms,
we still have a long way to go.

21:34.751 --> 21:36.086
You know that, right?

21:36.169 --> 21:38.922
Let's stay focused
on both artistic quality and public appeal

21:39.006 --> 21:42.009
and work toward winning
another award next year. Okay?

21:42.551 --> 21:45.220
On that note,
I'd like to add that yesterday…

21:45.304 --> 21:48.265
He might be avoiding me. Fair enough.

21:48.765 --> 21:51.518
-Aren't we all blessed with work!
-I know, right?

21:51.601 --> 21:54.688
I feel bad for Mr. Park.
You've already got so much on your plate.

21:54.771 --> 21:55.605
I know.

21:55.689 --> 21:58.233
It's still a good thing.
I'll take things one at a time.

21:58.317 --> 22:01.361
Anyway, are you doing okay?
That event looks like a lot of work.

22:01.445 --> 22:04.281
It is. That's why you should help me out.

22:04.990 --> 22:05.949
I'd be happy to.

22:07.200 --> 22:11.121
We're not even on the same team,
so it's totally understandable.

22:11.204 --> 22:12.998
He's Park Kyeong-nam, after all.

22:13.081 --> 22:13.915
Oh, right.

22:19.129 --> 22:20.964
Let's pick this up when we get there.

22:21.048 --> 22:22.049
Okay.

22:22.132 --> 22:23.884
I'm going to have some makgeolli.

22:23.967 --> 22:25.052
You know I don't drink.

22:25.135 --> 22:27.304
-Come on. That's not fair.
-Come on.

22:27.387 --> 22:29.222
-Yeah, drink with us.
-Damn it!

22:29.306 --> 22:30.307
You're no fun.

22:32.434 --> 22:33.518
Wait a minute.

22:34.353 --> 22:36.021
Why am I avoiding him?

22:50.285 --> 22:53.372
Can't we just have dinner tomorrow?
It's cold today.

22:54.623 --> 22:58.293
I'll be there within 30 minutes.
Wait there. I think I took the wrong turn.

22:58.377 --> 23:01.380
Hey, come on… Let me…

23:01.963 --> 23:03.173
Seriously?

23:03.256 --> 23:05.342
Hey, just let me in!

23:08.595 --> 23:10.347
I'll wait for you at the café.

23:13.725 --> 23:15.018
Hello, Ms. Seo.

23:15.102 --> 23:17.771
Hello. What brings you here?

23:17.854 --> 23:20.023
I'm here for a meeting with Kyeong-nam.

23:23.402 --> 23:25.153
Your latte is ready.

23:26.238 --> 23:27.322
Damn it.

23:29.741 --> 23:32.411
Yes. It's just like Park Kyeong-nam said.

23:32.494 --> 23:35.330
I'm not the one who got rejected.
I don't have to keep this up.

23:44.673 --> 23:46.007
Be confident.

23:47.676 --> 23:49.094
Stand tall.

23:51.555 --> 23:52.722
And smile.

23:55.100 --> 23:57.394
What? Too pretty to handle?

24:10.157 --> 24:12.576
Are you okay? That was really loud.

24:14.536 --> 24:15.871
I'm totally fine.

24:16.455 --> 24:18.206
It was just loud, that's all.

24:22.377 --> 24:25.881
Code red. Where are you?
I'm gonna wait outside.

24:27.716 --> 24:30.552
How come?
I'll be at least another 20 minutes.

24:30.635 --> 24:33.305
Hey, it's freezing outside.
Just stay there.

24:33.388 --> 24:34.723
I'll be there soon.

24:40.395 --> 24:41.354
Are you leaving?

24:42.063 --> 24:44.232
Oh, I just need to use the restroom.

24:48.528 --> 24:49.821
I'm worried about her.

24:56.203 --> 24:57.245
What is this?

24:57.954 --> 24:59.372
When did this show up?

25:03.210 --> 25:04.794
What am I gonna do?

25:11.968 --> 25:12.969
Goodbye.

25:14.054 --> 25:15.555
Put some ointment on that, okay?

25:20.185 --> 25:21.520
She's so scatterbrained.

25:21.603 --> 25:23.772
She's going to hit her head again soon.

25:23.855 --> 25:25.106
Where were we?

25:28.026 --> 25:29.027
Hold on a second.

25:42.958 --> 25:43.792
Look alike much?

25:51.800 --> 25:53.343
I'm so sorry.

25:53.426 --> 25:56.972
I think I've turned my blinker on
a hundred times on my way here.

25:57.889 --> 25:58.723
Hey!

25:58.807 --> 25:59.933
What happened there?

26:00.600 --> 26:01.851
Did you get into a fight?

26:01.935 --> 26:03.103
No.

26:03.603 --> 26:06.481
-Hey, let's just get out of here. Hurry!
-Okay.

26:07.482 --> 26:10.360
Goddamn it,
that was freaking embarrassing!

26:10.443 --> 26:12.445
Hey, come on. Let's go.

26:12.529 --> 26:13.363
Okay.

26:13.446 --> 26:14.531
-Go!
-Okay.

26:20.537 --> 26:21.371
Here.

26:22.414 --> 26:23.248
Thanks.

26:27.252 --> 26:29.254
Hey, just laugh out loud.

26:33.675 --> 26:34.843
Hold up.

26:34.926 --> 26:37.470
You got hit pretty hard.
Just how were you walking?

26:37.554 --> 26:40.932
Hey. If you hadn't brought your car
and ended up being late…

26:41.850 --> 26:42.684
Forget it.

26:43.393 --> 26:47.314
I was only trying to let you ride along
in comfort on this cold day.

26:48.982 --> 26:51.318
How are you even free today?
No more blind dates?

26:51.401 --> 26:52.235
Huh?

26:55.155 --> 26:57.073
I'm just taking a break.

26:58.908 --> 26:59.909
How come?

27:00.452 --> 27:02.871
I don't know.
I just think it's a waste of time.

27:05.332 --> 27:06.791
Someone's a copycat.

27:08.585 --> 27:11.421
I mean, I get dolled up
early in the morning

27:11.504 --> 27:14.883
just to see a guy I don't even like,
acting all cute and polite.

27:14.966 --> 27:17.844
Then I get home, wash off my makeup,
and feel so pathetic.

27:17.927 --> 27:22.682
"Am I wasting my peak years?"
That's how it makes me feel.

27:22.766 --> 27:25.435
Could there be something more fun
than dating in the world,

27:25.518 --> 27:27.520
and I'm the only one
who doesn't know about it?

27:27.604 --> 27:30.357
Hey, starting now,
you should look into that.

27:31.858 --> 27:35.487
Nope. I don't think
there's anything more fun than dating.

27:36.696 --> 27:39.282
It's just that it's so damn hard
to find a guy I like!

27:41.159 --> 27:43.495
Are you talking to yourself?
Why ask if you had an answer?

27:43.995 --> 27:46.831
Anyway, think about
how you're going to deal with that.

27:46.915 --> 27:48.333
You can't go to work like that.

27:58.093 --> 28:01.513
Perfect. It's just perfect.
You can't tell at all.

28:01.596 --> 28:02.430
Really?

28:06.309 --> 28:08.978
Seriously? I think it's pretty obvious.

28:09.771 --> 28:11.022
Should I just cut my bangs?

28:12.273 --> 28:15.318
Don't you know that 97% of women
who get bangs regret it right away?

28:15.902 --> 28:19.781
As soon as you get them, it becomes
your goal to grow your hair out again.

28:19.864 --> 28:21.408
You'll thank me later.

28:28.248 --> 28:31.334
You got a haircut? It looks good on you.

28:31.418 --> 28:33.169
-Very nice.
-Thank you.

28:33.253 --> 28:34.504
It suits you well.

28:34.587 --> 28:36.339
-Oh my God!
-Wow.

28:38.967 --> 28:39.801
What's going on?

28:40.301 --> 28:41.803
Oh, is it a wig?

28:42.637 --> 28:43.722
Does it show?

28:43.805 --> 28:45.181
A little from up close.

28:46.433 --> 28:48.643
What happened?
Are you going for a new look?

28:49.602 --> 28:50.437
Huh?

28:51.813 --> 28:53.815
No, it's not like that.

28:53.898 --> 28:56.901
I just felt
like changing things up a little.

29:10.999 --> 29:12.333
Hello.

29:18.757 --> 29:19.841
What do we have here?

29:20.967 --> 29:22.385
A sudden change in hairstyle?

29:32.270 --> 29:34.272
God, so embarrassing.

29:36.983 --> 29:37.901
You crazy bitch…

29:37.984 --> 29:41.154
I honestly wasn't going to bring this up.

29:42.071 --> 29:43.865
-What?
-Are you not over me yet?

29:43.948 --> 29:45.492
You crazy bitch!

29:48.453 --> 29:49.287
Ms. Yun.

29:49.370 --> 29:51.247
-Are you okay?
-What do you mean?

29:51.331 --> 29:55.543
You've been having these random outbursts
for the last few days,

29:55.627 --> 29:57.128
which is a little strange.

29:57.212 --> 29:58.046
Huh?

29:58.129 --> 30:00.632
You were the one who secretly left snacks
in front of my room.

30:00.715 --> 30:02.634
Hold it right there. That was…

30:02.717 --> 30:03.635
-Those were…
-What?

30:04.219 --> 30:05.637
Those were meant for So-yeong!

30:11.267 --> 30:13.728
So-yeong, just go. Get out.

30:13.812 --> 30:15.563
I'm really struggling right now. Go.

30:15.647 --> 30:16.981
Okay.

30:22.487 --> 30:24.405
Are you kidding me?

30:29.828 --> 30:32.080
I'll give you just ten more minutes.

30:45.844 --> 30:46.803
What?

30:54.686 --> 30:55.937
God, it's cold.

30:58.523 --> 31:01.025
Come on. Don't do this to me!

31:04.821 --> 31:05.989
Just 30 more minutes.

31:06.781 --> 31:07.991
Seriously?

31:08.533 --> 31:10.326
It's always 30 minutes with her.

31:18.251 --> 31:19.085
Cold!

31:27.802 --> 31:28.636
Oh God…

31:41.858 --> 31:43.276
I was cold too.

31:56.039 --> 31:57.749
This was the only heater we had.

32:00.960 --> 32:02.295
Oh, but…

32:04.797 --> 32:07.091
You said you were cold too.

32:07.592 --> 32:08.801
Let's share it.

32:21.439 --> 32:23.191
How's that bump from yesterday?

32:24.025 --> 32:27.028
Oh, it's gone down a lot.

32:30.615 --> 32:31.532
That's a relief.

32:41.125 --> 32:44.796
Dong-min said you guys came back to Seoul
later than usual on Sunday.

32:44.879 --> 32:46.714
I guess you had a lot of fun.

32:48.466 --> 32:49.884
Yes, well,

32:49.968 --> 32:52.387
we saw the ocean and had some good food.

32:54.889 --> 32:55.723
We just…

32:56.516 --> 32:57.433
Yeah.

32:58.518 --> 33:01.604
I saw the pictures,
and I was really jealous.

33:01.688 --> 33:06.192
Ms. Yun wanted to come back early,
so I had to eat ramyeon at the airport.

33:08.820 --> 33:10.154
Then did you

33:11.447 --> 33:12.782
want to stay longer?

33:23.751 --> 33:24.585
Well…

33:25.294 --> 33:28.673
Yes, I wanted to stay
and have good food as well.

33:29.966 --> 33:32.969
Next time,
I plan on staying a little longer.

33:36.764 --> 33:37.765
I see.

33:47.775 --> 33:48.609
UPLOAD COMPLETE

34:23.853 --> 34:25.730
I'll see you tomorrow.

34:26.481 --> 34:27.315
Right.

35:04.519 --> 35:07.772
I WANTED TO TELL YOU THAT I LIKE YOU

36:03.786 --> 36:06.789
I wanted to tell you that I like you.

36:18.009 --> 36:19.510
Did you get my letter?

36:21.137 --> 36:23.389
This is kind of embarrassing.

36:23.472 --> 36:24.390
What's this?

36:24.473 --> 36:25.308
To be honest,

36:26.684 --> 36:28.186
I was a little mad at you.

36:28.895 --> 36:31.939
For not even answering me
when I asked you to come with me.

36:33.191 --> 36:36.027
So I was just going to get over you, but

36:37.236 --> 36:38.613
it's harder than I thought.

36:40.865 --> 36:41.949
I miss you.

37:24.867 --> 37:26.661
1: PLANC
2: THE MAN TO KNOW

37:30.498 --> 37:32.833
TMTK was number one forever until today.

37:32.917 --> 37:35.419
-Once you slip, it's all downhill.
-Deepest condolences.

37:35.503 --> 37:38.005
-It lasted longer than expected.
-Hwany sure is no joke.

37:38.089 --> 37:40.174
Isn't this the first time
she got dethroned?

37:41.467 --> 37:44.053
Winning an award sure does help a lot,
doesn't it?

37:44.136 --> 37:45.388
Don't get excited just yet.

37:45.471 --> 37:47.974
Would it kill you to play along for once?

37:48.057 --> 37:50.142
You saw what happened to me in Busan.

37:50.935 --> 37:53.104
What are you doing tomorrow?
Let's get a drink.

37:53.187 --> 37:54.105
Aren't you working?

37:54.188 --> 37:57.817
This calls for a proper celebration.
I might lose my spot next week, after all.

37:59.235 --> 38:00.736
Okay. I'll get back to you.

38:14.917 --> 38:17.378
-Yeah. I had absolutely no idea.
-I know.

38:18.379 --> 38:19.463
Hey!

38:19.547 --> 38:21.215
-Hi, Mi-rae.
-Hi.

38:29.181 --> 38:30.433
Are you okay?

38:32.018 --> 38:33.519
Yup, I'm okay.

38:34.020 --> 38:37.189
It happens all the time.
Don't worry about it too much.

38:37.273 --> 38:38.107
Sure.

38:38.190 --> 38:40.359
It can make it back to the top!

38:40.443 --> 38:41.444
Definitely.

38:41.527 --> 38:44.780
Sure, they are going to keep
trading places,

38:44.864 --> 38:48.200
but all you need is for the author
to keep her head. Right?

38:58.127 --> 38:58.961
Oh man.

39:02.590 --> 39:06.302
Cheer up, it's okay. These things happen.

39:06.385 --> 39:10.181
PlanC won a big award,
and it got a lot of press, after all.

39:14.268 --> 39:15.186
Mr. Hwang.

39:15.269 --> 39:16.979
So what's the game plan now?

39:18.189 --> 39:20.566
-What?
-You do have a plan, don't you?

39:21.984 --> 39:24.570
Oh, right. Well, I…

39:24.653 --> 39:28.532
I'll put in the work with Ms. Yun
to give it our best shot.

39:29.617 --> 39:30.618
Hey, Seo Mi-rae.

39:31.952 --> 39:35.247
Do you have any idea how much
the coin sales for TMTK have fallen?

39:36.040 --> 39:37.041
What?

39:38.209 --> 39:40.336
Yun Song's contract is almost up.

39:40.419 --> 39:43.714
At this rate, we'll never renew
the contract on good terms.

39:43.798 --> 39:46.384
Her next season
would have to be the final one.

39:47.176 --> 39:50.513
You have other authors to manage.
Stop letting her drag you around.

39:50.596 --> 39:52.014
It's exhausting.

39:52.098 --> 39:55.434
I'll talk to her and see what I can do.

39:56.018 --> 39:59.146
Okay. So how?
How will you talk to her about it?

39:59.897 --> 40:00.731
Excuse me?

40:03.359 --> 40:04.568
So you're clueless.

40:06.070 --> 40:08.989
Hey, you're not blameless here.
You know that?

40:09.073 --> 40:12.993
If the producer gives it everything,
the title doesn't sink so easily.

40:13.077 --> 40:15.329
But look at what you've done!

40:15.413 --> 40:17.081
She's our most expensive author,

40:17.164 --> 40:19.667
and look what happened
in just a few months.

40:19.750 --> 40:21.001
I'm sorry, sir.

40:24.839 --> 40:25.756
Hello?

40:33.722 --> 40:34.807
I'm not sure.

40:34.890 --> 40:37.601
She hasn't been lashing out as usual,
and she's being quiet.

40:41.272 --> 40:43.023
I'll come over tomorrow.

40:43.732 --> 40:44.817
I said go.

40:45.818 --> 40:47.736
Your words of comfort
won't change a thing.

40:48.612 --> 40:50.364
Just throw a fit instead.

40:51.532 --> 40:54.076
I knew this day would come eventually.

40:55.119 --> 40:56.704
It's a downward spiral.

40:57.371 --> 40:58.873
That's all there is to it.

41:01.417 --> 41:02.543
Ms. Yun.

41:04.795 --> 41:06.338
I told you, didn't I?

41:07.381 --> 41:10.885
I only blew up because of Choi Si-woo.
I don't have what it takes.

41:13.304 --> 41:15.222
It's time for me to put it all down.

41:16.265 --> 41:19.935
Sell my car, sell my home,

41:20.728 --> 41:22.813
and sell… the building.

41:23.731 --> 41:26.567
What's this about selling stuff?

41:26.650 --> 41:27.485
Ms. Yun.

41:27.568 --> 41:30.613
I'm not going to give up
on TMTK like this.

41:30.696 --> 41:33.908
It's true that I was distracted
by some personal stuff,

41:33.991 --> 41:37.703
and I'm sorry I couldn't give it
everything I've got.

41:37.786 --> 41:39.079
What personal stuff?

41:40.539 --> 41:41.832
You slacked off, didn't you?

41:41.916 --> 41:44.418
No, it's not like that. I…

41:45.169 --> 41:48.506
Anyway, I'm going to go all-in
from now on.

41:48.589 --> 41:51.884
So I need you to get a grip too. Okay?

41:51.967 --> 41:56.639
I'll do whatever it takes
to get TMTK back to number one.

41:57.681 --> 41:58.516
Really?

42:00.142 --> 42:03.562
So let's go eat something nice today.

42:03.646 --> 42:04.897
My treat!

42:05.397 --> 42:06.398
You're buying?

42:06.482 --> 42:08.150
It's on me today!

42:08.651 --> 42:10.653
PLANC
THE MAN TO KNOW

42:10.736 --> 42:13.614
Stop looking. Don't you get tired of it?

42:13.697 --> 42:17.660
Back when Mr. Cho got me and Yun Song
office spaces in the same building,

42:17.743 --> 42:21.455
he put me in the semi-basement
and her on the top floor. Did I tell you?

42:21.539 --> 42:22.873
A hundred times.

42:22.957 --> 42:26.418
I've been dreaming of this moment
since then.

42:26.502 --> 42:27.962
So stop being such a buzzkill.

42:28.546 --> 42:30.256
Fine. Enjoy it.

42:31.298 --> 42:32.800
But I feel bad for Ms. Seo.

42:34.677 --> 42:36.011
Do you think she's upset?

42:40.307 --> 42:41.392
I'm sure she is.

42:42.560 --> 42:45.396
God, it's freezing.
Why did we come all the way out here?

42:45.479 --> 42:46.981
How am I supposed to get home?

42:47.064 --> 42:49.233
You never get out of your neighborhood.

42:49.316 --> 42:50.818
They have amazing food here.

42:50.901 --> 42:52.778
What is this place? It's freezing.

42:53.487 --> 42:56.073
You can have whatever you want today!

42:57.741 --> 42:58.909
Isn't that Park?

43:01.954 --> 43:03.539
Damn it, let's go somewhere else.

43:03.622 --> 43:05.666
Ms. Yun. Hello.

43:07.668 --> 43:09.628
-Hello.
-Hi.

43:09.712 --> 43:11.046
Hello.

43:11.130 --> 43:14.967
Hwany's studio is around here, right?
Is this a celebration?

43:15.050 --> 43:17.970
We just had a meeting. What about you?

43:19.013 --> 43:21.307
We just came here to clear our heads.

43:23.350 --> 43:25.269
-How are you doing?
-Not well.

43:25.352 --> 43:27.021
-Cool.
-Damn it.

43:27.104 --> 43:29.898
-I said let's go.
-Right. We'll be going now.

43:29.982 --> 43:31.191
Annoying prick.

43:31.275 --> 43:33.402
Hell, we should have left before they did.

43:34.820 --> 43:35.988
Ms. Yun!

43:51.754 --> 43:53.464
I'm sorry I'm late.

43:53.547 --> 43:54.798
We're going somewhere else.

43:54.882 --> 43:56.884
-What? Where?
-Let's go.

43:56.967 --> 43:58.510
Wait!

44:01.847 --> 44:02.765
Wait a second.

44:11.940 --> 44:14.151
-Let me--
-No, I insist.

44:17.613 --> 44:18.739
Have some of this.

44:19.281 --> 44:21.367
-Thank you.
-No problem.

44:21.450 --> 44:24.078
What the heck is wrong with him?

44:25.954 --> 44:28.290
Hey, we'll be leaving soon. Keep it on.

44:28.374 --> 44:29.625
Man, such an eyesore.

44:29.708 --> 44:31.418
Oh, we're leaving soon?

44:32.544 --> 44:34.129
I'll just use the bathroom, then.

44:34.213 --> 44:35.214
Sure.

44:39.051 --> 44:40.636
Excuse me.

44:40.719 --> 44:43.722
Can you not ruin the mood?
You're making her walk on eggshells!

44:43.806 --> 44:46.684
Stop picking a fight.
I'll just take So-yeong and leave.

44:46.767 --> 44:49.812
Hey, that's just low. You can't do that.

44:49.895 --> 44:52.022
Why can't I do that?

44:52.106 --> 44:55.025
What will you offer to make us stay?
You going on hiatus?

44:55.818 --> 44:57.736
-Hiatus?
-Yeah!

44:59.988 --> 45:01.532
Sure. Yeah, I would--

45:03.826 --> 45:05.285
-Hey.
-What?

45:05.369 --> 45:09.707
Don't be so difficult.
We're negotiating as authors here.

45:10.374 --> 45:11.208
Ms. Yun.

45:11.709 --> 45:14.086
I'll do whatever you want.
Just don't take So-yeong.

45:14.712 --> 45:16.630
-Come on.
-Did you hear that?

45:17.840 --> 45:19.007
Please stop.

45:19.091 --> 45:21.635
Stop what?
You said we should do whatever it takes.

45:23.971 --> 45:25.222
So when are we leaving?

45:25.305 --> 45:26.849
What? We're not.

45:27.683 --> 45:28.684
What?

45:28.767 --> 45:30.853
The food here is good. You should eat up.

45:30.936 --> 45:33.564
-It's hot in here. Take off your coat.
-You should.

45:34.064 --> 45:35.357
Raise our glasses?

45:35.441 --> 45:36.984
-Yes!
-All right.

45:38.193 --> 45:39.027
Good stuff.

45:39.111 --> 45:41.155
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

45:41.655 --> 45:43.115
Goodness.

45:50.038 --> 45:52.750
There. Let's drink hard.

45:53.250 --> 45:55.335
Yeah, drink away.

45:55.419 --> 45:56.545
-Let's go!
-Let's go!

46:01.258 --> 46:03.010
Drink milk in the morning…

46:03.093 --> 46:04.011
Milk!

46:04.511 --> 46:05.345
She drinks milk.

46:06.722 --> 46:07.556
Oh, really?

46:08.515 --> 46:10.434
To like someone…

46:10.517 --> 46:13.937
Forward, into the heart of the enemy!

46:14.021 --> 46:15.272
It's here.

46:18.025 --> 46:20.194
…means coming up with excuses…

46:23.572 --> 46:24.573
Yes?

46:25.157 --> 46:28.494
Would you like to borrow this?
You can take your time returning it.

46:28.577 --> 46:30.829
-Oh, if you don't mind…
-Okay.

46:30.913 --> 46:33.415
…to spend more time together.

46:33.499 --> 46:37.085
So, So-yeong, this Christmas…

46:38.545 --> 46:39.922
Chris…

46:43.842 --> 46:45.135
Do you have plans for Christmas?

46:45.719 --> 46:48.931
Well, I guess I'll be watching anime
and movies at home.

46:49.014 --> 46:50.098
In that case--

46:50.182 --> 46:51.600
Sheesh, nowadays,

46:51.683 --> 46:54.853
the younger ones
are living duller lives than us.

46:54.937 --> 46:57.523
And your life is such a barrel of laughs?

46:57.606 --> 46:59.191
Have you got plans for Christmas?

46:59.274 --> 47:01.985
Hey, didn't I say last time
that I have a boyfriend?

47:02.069 --> 47:03.737
I told you.

47:03.821 --> 47:05.489
Right. So you said.

47:05.572 --> 47:07.241
You don't believe me, do you?

47:07.324 --> 47:09.743
Seo here even talked to my boyfriend
on the phone.

47:09.827 --> 47:11.620
-Right?
-Yes.

47:12.538 --> 47:13.372
Wait, really?

47:14.081 --> 47:14.915
Yes.

47:15.457 --> 47:17.209
He seemed to really like her.

47:18.877 --> 47:22.631
How do you find the time to meet him?
You're always working.

47:22.714 --> 47:23.549
Huh?

47:24.633 --> 47:25.717
You know, I just

47:26.218 --> 47:29.054
make do with what little time I can spare.

47:29.555 --> 47:33.350
Anyway, so am I the only one here
dating someone?

47:33.976 --> 47:37.396
What's wrong with all of you?
You're in your prime.

47:37.479 --> 47:39.064
Whatever.

47:39.731 --> 47:41.608
I'm jealous. So jealous.

47:42.442 --> 47:44.862
I think I'll just have more snacks.

47:48.323 --> 47:50.659
Damn it. It slipped my mind.

47:51.952 --> 47:53.453
We're out of snacks.

47:55.622 --> 47:57.624
We're also out of booze.

47:58.375 --> 48:00.043
Go get some more liquor.

48:20.147 --> 48:21.982
I…

48:24.651 --> 48:26.486
I'm sorry I lied to you.

48:28.280 --> 48:29.615
Lied to me about what?

48:31.241 --> 48:32.075
Well…

48:32.993 --> 48:36.246
You know,
how I told you that I had a boyfriend.

48:39.833 --> 48:42.836
I didn't mean to lie to you,

48:42.920 --> 48:47.257
but I'd never been in that situation
before, so I was panicking a little.

48:51.428 --> 48:52.346
I'm sorry too.

48:54.598 --> 48:55.432
What?

48:56.850 --> 49:00.312
I should've known bringing up my feelings
like that would make you uncomfortable,

49:01.271 --> 49:02.606
but I only thought of myself.

49:09.279 --> 49:11.365
Thank you for saying that.

49:12.532 --> 49:15.702
To be honest, recently,
it has been bothering me a bit.

49:16.370 --> 49:17.204
I kept

49:17.913 --> 49:21.625
thinking about how you said you were upset
before we left for Busan.

49:24.169 --> 49:25.504
I'm not upset anymore.

49:29.299 --> 49:30.175
Really?

49:32.552 --> 49:33.720
That's good.

49:39.643 --> 49:40.811
Ms. Seo.

49:42.854 --> 49:43.689
Yes?

49:46.108 --> 49:46.942
Now…

49:49.528 --> 49:52.030
is it official
that you don't have a boyfriend?

49:57.995 --> 49:59.830
Can I act like I'm also in the know?

50:03.208 --> 50:04.710
Yes, I guess so.

50:10.173 --> 50:11.091
From now on…

50:18.765 --> 50:20.517
can I do as I please?

53:41.259 --> 53:46.264
Subtitle translation by: Daham Yoon
